commit message:
Convert tools now use uppercase hex.

Bugfix: Removed leading empty line of a dump (raw-dump2mct-dump.sh).
Updated the code import section of README.md.
Fixed parse issue for to big/small integers (in value block tool).
Updated readme and Help & Info section.
Changed layout of write dump to support multiple options.

Added infos on the new feature (use static ACs).
Updated the help and info section (in-app help).
Rewrote 'no Mifare Classic support' message to be more clear.

New release: 1.5.0

Updated changelog.
Increased version number.
